messages.content: We make solid gold custom pieces like this with our craftsmen in their home workshop. Let me know more about what you're imagining in terms of aesthetic & budget and we can discuss detail to see if we're a fit !
Congratulations on your wedding plans - exciting!
Hi kak Indira, salam kenal juga!

Hi! Salam kenal, aku Indira. Aku ada rencana mau bikin wedding rings, and jewelry pieces for a wedding kemungkinan di Agustus 2024 sudah ready. Aku mau discuss lebih lanjut untuk T&C nya ya. Thank you!
